 (Abigail Morris) 在 7 月 4 日即将到来的英国大选中发表讲话</a>，要求选民“互相保护，要有一些他妈的同理心”。</p><h2> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kasabian-glastonbury-2024-secret-set-watch-interview-footage-photos-3770249">卡萨比安确认伍西的秘密设置</a></h2><p>关于<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kasabian">Kasabian</a>在格拉斯顿伯里秘密演出的谣言持续数周后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-kasabian-confirm-rumoured-secret-set-3770077">莱斯特乐队终于在周六下午确认</a>，他们将于下午 6 点在 Woodsies 演出。 </p><figure id="attachment_3770274" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3770274" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3770274" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-69170_EDIT.jpg" alt="Kasabian 在 Glastonbury 2024 现场演出。图片来源：NME 的 Andy Ford" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-69170_EDIT.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-69170_EDIT-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-69170_EDIT-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-69170_EDIT-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-69170_EDIT-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-69170_EDIT-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3770274" class="wp-caption-text"> Kasabian 在 Glastonbury 2024 现场演出。图片来源：NME 的 Andy Ford</figcaption></figure><p>演出前，现场非常拥挤，以至于歌迷们都被拒之门外，主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/serge-pizzorno">谢尔盖·皮佐诺 (Serge Pizzorno)</a>在演出前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kasabian-glastonbury-2024-secret-set-watch-interview-footage-photos-3770249">接受<em>NME</em>采访</a>时承诺“这是一个充满力量的时刻”。 “我们正在尽力塞进去，”他补充道。 “我们有几首新曲目在现场表现得非常好，这太荒谬了。我们进进出出。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kasabian-glastonbury-2024-secret-set-watch-interview-footage-photos-3770249">阅读<em>《NME》对 Pizzorno 的</em>采访</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-kasabian-cover-bangers-play-classics-and-preview-happenings-at-packed-out-glastonbury-2024-secret-set-3770215">回顾 Kasabian 在 Woodsies 的喧闹秘密</a>。 </p><p><iframe title="Kasabian 在 Glastonbury 2024 的秘密演出中与 Noel Fielding 一起放松" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/B8ipAZm1Q30?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h2> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/camila-cabello-glastonbury-live-review-setlist-photos-3770276">卡米拉·卡贝洛 (Camila Cabello) 在另一个舞台上展示新专辑《C,XOXO》</a> </h2><figure id="attachment_3770297" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3770297" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3770297" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_CamillaCabello_Other_AFord-620472.jpg" alt="卡米拉·卡贝洛" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_CamillaCabello_Other_AFord-620472.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_CamillaCabello_Other_AFord-620472-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_CamillaCabello_Other_AFord-620472-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_CamillaCabello_Other_AFord-620472-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_CamillaCabello_Other_AFord-620472-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_CamillaCabello_Other_AFord-620472-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3770297" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：《NME》安迪·福特</figcaption></figure><p>发行第四张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/camila-cabello-c-xoxo-album-review-3768433">《C,XOXO》</a>一天后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/camila-cabello">卡米拉·卡贝洛 (Camila Cabello)</a>在另一个舞台上展示了​​这张专辑，并辅以身着 Cyber​​dog 风格服装的舞蹈和精心设计的舞台布景，包括金属秋千和 BMX 特技坡道。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/camila-cabello-glastonbury-live-review-setlist-photos-3770276">阅读<em>NME 对 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 Camila Cabello 的</em>三星级评论</a>。</p><h2> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-fat-white-family-mock-idles-joe-talbot-3770205">Fat White Family 的 Lias Saoudi 向 IDLES 的 Joe Talbot 发起攻击</a></h2><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fat-white-family">Fat White Family 的</a>Lias Saoudi 在 Woodsies 演出期间对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idles">IDLES</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joe-talbot">Joe Talbot</a>进行了猛烈攻击。在演奏歌曲《我是马克·E·史密斯》之前，萨乌迪干巴巴地宣布：“这是一首关于我的女权主义热情的歌曲——它的名字是《我是乔·塔尔博特》。”</p><p>在前一天<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/idles-glastonbury-2024-other-stage-review-setlist-photos-3769997">《IDLES》的 Glasto 场景</a>中，塔尔博特带领大家高呼“Fuck the King！”在胖白家族的场景中，萨乌迪说道：“上帝保佑国王！滚蛋吧。”</p><h2> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/orbital-bring-out-mel-c-and-tilda-swinton-as-special-guests-at-glastonbury-2024-3770173">轨道乐队带来梅尔·C 和蒂尔达·斯文顿</a></h2><p>传奇舞蹈组合<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/orbital">Orbital</a>第七次在格拉斯顿伯里演出，并邀请了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spice-girls">辣妹</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/melanie-c">Mel C</a>和女演员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tilda-swinton">蒂尔达·斯文顿 (Tilda Swinton)</a>出席。斯温顿以《Deeper》帮助 Orbital 开启了演出，而这位前 Sporty Spice 后来也加入了二人组的《Spicy》，其中采样了 Spice Girls 的曲目，包括她们的热门歌曲《Wannabe》。</p><h2> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/disclosure-bring-out-sam-smith-as-special-guest-during-glastonbury-2024-set-3770351">披露邀请萨姆·史密斯演唱《Latch》</a></h2><p>流行歌星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-smith">萨姆·史密斯 (Sam Smith)</a>在 The Other Stage 的闭场演出中加入了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/disclosure">Disclosure</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/disclosure-bring-out-sam-smith-as-special-guest-during-glastonbury-2024-set-3770351">，演唱了他们合作的 2013 年突破歌曲《Latch》，并翻唱了 Faithless 的经典歌曲《Insomnia》</a> 。</p><h2> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-tom-cruise-simon-pegg-lead-crowd-singing-oasis-dont-look-back-in-anger-before-coldplay-set-3770423">汤姆·克鲁斯和西蒙·佩吉在酷玩乐队演出前加入观众的绿洲合唱</a></h2><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-cruise">汤姆·克鲁斯</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/simon-pegg">西蒙·佩吉</a>被拍到在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">酷玩乐队</a>演出前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-tom-cruise-simon-pegg-lead-crowd-singing-oasis-dont-look-back-in-anger-before-coldplay-set-3770423">与众人一起合唱《愤怒中的别回头》</a> 。</p><p>站在金字塔舞台的平台上， <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/mission-impossible"><em>《碟中谍》的</em></a>联合主演们与导演克里斯·麦夸里和女演员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gillian-anderson">吉莉安·安德森</a>一起欣赏<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲</a>热门歌曲的演唱，佩吉戏剧性地做出了指挥家的手势。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="西蒙·佩吉和埃德加·赖特在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节：为什么没有《僵尸肖恩 2》" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SZPJ_vEfDw0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h2> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-heres-what-coldplay-played-for-record-breaking-headline-set-3770328">酷玩乐队 (Coldplay) 在格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 (Glastonbury) 上演第五次打破纪录的头条新闻，带来了小西姆兹 (Little Simz) 和迈克尔·J·福克斯 (Michael J. Fox)</a> </h2><figure id="attachment_3770420" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3770420" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3770420" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/coldplay-glastonbury-2024-chris-martin-credit-samir-