山姆·史密斯 (Sam Smith) 出任格拉斯顿伯里 2024 年特邀嘉宾https://www.nme.com/news/music/disclosure-bring-out-sam-smith-as-special-guest-during-glastonbury-2024-set-3770351?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=disclosure-bring-萨姆·史密斯在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里期间担任特邀嘉宾Anagricel DuranSat, 29 Jun 2024 23:26:13 +0000 Music NewsNewsElectronicPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3770351 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>两人还翻唱了 Faithless 的《Insomnia》</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/disclosure-bring-out-sam-smith-as-special-guest-during-glastonbury-2024-set-3770351">《Disclosure》报道指出 Sam Smith 作为 Glastonbury 2024 演出的特邀嘉宾，</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发表。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Disclosure">《Disclosure》</a>让<a href="/artists/Sam-Smith">萨姆·史密斯 (Sam Smith)</a>作为今年<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节现场的惊喜嘉宾。</a></p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-liveblog-news-updates-reviews-rumours-photo-video-3769371">格拉斯顿伯里 2024 年现场博客：周六的所有活动</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位歌手与电子二人组一起在 Other 舞台上现场表演了他们 2013 年的合作曲目“Latch”。史密斯身穿全黑运动服，留着胡须，出现并接管了这首歌的主唱。</p><p> “所以大家听着，大约八年前我们在这个舞台上唱了另一首歌。我觉得你们中的一些人可能想听一首歌曲。有人知道那首歌可能是什么吗？这是一首永远改变了我们生活的歌曲，”霍华德·劳伦斯在谈到这对二人组合时说道。</p><p>他继续说道：“伤口有点深。哦，还有一件事，请欢迎 Sam Smith 上台！” </p><p></p><figure id="attachment_3770371" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3770371" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3770371" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-during-Disclosure-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit_-BBC-Iplayer-screen-grab.jpg" alt="萨姆·史密斯 (Sam Smith) 在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节披露期间。图片来源：BBC Iplayer 屏幕截图。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-during-Disclosure-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit_-BBC-Iplayer-screen-grab.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-during-Disclosure-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit_-BBC-Iplayer-screen-grab-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-during-Disclosure-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit_-BBC-Iplayer-screen-grab-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-during-Disclosure-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit_-BBC-Iplayer-screen-grab-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-during-Disclosure-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit_-BBC-Iplayer-screen-grab-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Sam-Smith-duri